    <sampling_method>Non-Probability Sample</sampling_method>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  Relapsing-remitting multiple scelrosis (RRMS) and secondary progressive multiple
             sclerosis (SPMS) patients

          -  Having Betaferon treatment, including patients who are

               -  First time using; or

               -  Re-staring; or

               -  Switching from other diseases modifying drugs (DMDs)

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  Known or newly identified contraindication for administration of Betaferon according
             to Summary of Product Characteristic (SmPC).
      </textblock>
    </criteria>
